{"tid":2059671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【灰機文】35+初選睇個勢都係搞唔成 - 白頭佬最開心, 一舊雲最安心","createTime":"2020-06-11T05:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:50:48.000Z","uid":278396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6414a25c0c19ee54c80bf9429de1be345b162c0","tid":2059671,"uid":278396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"區軒同戴耀廷搞民主派初選，好多人諗住借呢個機會踢走白頭佬同一舊雲，再爭取35+。搞呢壇初選要350萬，為咗表示公正，佢地唔可以收政黨捐款，<span style=\"color: orange;\">結果經過2日，只籌得15萬幾&hellip; 得4%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要連天真戴耀廷都灰機埋... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/1416140878579669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBennyTaiHK%2Fposts%2F1416140878579669&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRGmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=df64ffd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BennyTaiHK/posts/1416140878579669</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然我天真戴耀廷有時真係好膠，但呢次我撐佢呀！<br />\n<br />\n大家再唔推，白頭佬同一舊雲必定入閘，跟住連35+都輸鳩埋。初選反應差，泛民就唔駛面對民意，共同綱領點解唔肯簽係因為我地俾唔到壓力佢地呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港進入左另一個抗爭階段喇，如果下屆坐係立法會既仲係白頭佬同 一舊雲，我地仲點玩呀？！</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n//你最後一次做愛的時候，不會知道那是你最後一次做愛。// 大家一定要珍惜每一次投票的機會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4bf453b11d87b64850653df0501a296f8f58f7c","tid":2059671,"uid":278396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"大家入去支持下啦：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/democrats35plus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fdemocrats35plus%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRGmu5